deck: Writer/Editor. Co-Creator of the series Jack of Spades at Source Point Press and Magma-man at the Michigan Comics Collective. He has written a graphic novel based on the psychobilly/rockabilly band, The Creepshow. He has had comic book short stories appear in the anthologies Serial #2 (Source Point Press), IF Powers... #2 (RIA Comics), MCC Volume II (Michigan Comics Collective) and 13 Little Hells (Michigan Comics Collective). HIs one-shot, Vostokapolis, was published by DimThroat Comics.
description: Trico Lutkins was one of the founders of Source Point Press. He co-created the ongoing series, Jack of Spades, with Joshua Werner. He created and wrote the limited series, Magman-Man, for the Michigan Comics Collective. He has also written short comics for Thirteen Little Hells (Michigan Comics Collective), Serial # 2 (Source Point Press}, If...Powers #2 (RIA Comics) and the Michigan Comics Collective Anthology Vol. II. His one-shot comic, Vostokapolis, was published by DimThroat Comics. He has written for Evolved Comics and Scape Goat Press.
name: Trico Lutkins
